"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li>",
"     <a class=\"nounderline abstract\" href=\"UTD.htm?21/40/22150/abstract/2\">",
"      Casey KR, Cantillo KO, Brown LK. Sleep-related hypoventilation/hypoxemic syndromes. Chest 2007; 131:1936.",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
