"     Phillipson EA, Bowes G. Control of breathing during sleep. In: Handbook of Physiology, Cherniack NS, Widdicombe JG (Eds), Section 3: The Respiratory System; Vol. II, Control of Breathing, American Physiologic Society, Bethesda, MD, 1986, pp. 649-689.",
